      "id": "PopularPost111896",
      "post_content": "It doesn't really work very well under the rules. It has to see the future and if the spell would destroy your land if it were to resolve right then, Equinox will counter it. A misfit relic from the days of interrupts, I guess. Or maybe it didn't really work under that clunky system, either. ",
